      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "That is a dangerous idea; relying solely on extra doses of an albuterol inhaler without a doctor's orders can mask a serious worsening of your condition and lead to a severe asthma attack. While traffic in Mumbai is stressful, ignoring escalating breathing difficulties to save time could result in emergency room visits that are much more time-consuming and costly. You should call an urologist online or your local clinic right away, as today might be the last chance to avoid a life-threatening situation.",
